My highlevel India checklist : 

- Hair (I don’t bother to research & establish a new relation with new hair stylist in India as I am pretty satisfied with my current one)
- deep clean home so we return back to a clean house 
- Indian wear & makeup donation (specific category of donation is so much worth taking it back to India vs donating in the US) 
- Empty clean refrigerator so we can come back home for a fresh restock 
- Indoor Plants have a water backup system 
- make a list of all the contents in the suitcase / take a pic with suitcase. (This has become very important especially as the family grew with more suitcases to pack. Not only this makes unpacking easy but also is a better system to ensure what’s in it / in case of lost baggage)

.
.
.
.
.
.
